
GetDenominations

Tells front end what money denominations are accepted
GET
http://localhost:9090/api/v1/payment
response
{
	"status": "SUCCESS",
	"code": null,
	"error": null,
	"data": {
		"change": 388,
		"changeAsDenominators": [
			200,
			100,
			50,
			20,
			10,
			5,
			2,
			1
		]
	}
}
==========================================================================================================================================
GetMoneyInTheMachine
Gets loaded money from the machine, was supposed to tell the person loading the machine what money is in the machine during loadup
GET
http://localhost:9090/api/v1/payment/moneyOnMachine
//MoneyDenominator:quantity
{
	"200": 10,
	"100": 10,
	"50": 10,
	"20": 10,
	"10": 10,
	"5": 10,
	"2": 10
}
==========================================================================================================================================
Pay
Get total from card and inserted money calculate change and provide denominations to dispensed
http://localhost:9090/api/v1/payment
POST
Request
{
	"cartTotal": 60,
	"moneyInserted":[
		100
	]
}
Response
{
	"status": "SUCCESS",
	"code": null,
	"error": null,
	"data": {
		"change": 40,
		"changeAsDenominators": [
			20,
			20
		]
	}
}
==========================================================================================================================================
Order
used on checkout and provide c
http://localhost:9090/api/v1/checkout

POST
Request
{
  "data": [
    {"id":1,"quantityRequired":3},
		{"id":2,"quantityRequired":3}
  ]
}

Response
{
	"status": "SUCCESS",
	"code": null,
	"error": null,
	"data": []
}
