==========================================================================================================================================
Dispense
Dispense change with the given denominators
http://localhost:9090/api/v1/dispense
Request
{
		"change": 40,
		"changeAsDenominators": [
			20,
			20
		]
}

Response
{
	"status": "SUCCESS",
	"code": null,
	"error": null
}
